host shell (or is empty if it isn’t defined).\n* The `>` redirection stays 
inside the container, but the file name it sees is something 
like\n\n```\n/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/games:/
usr/local/games:/home/raimondo/agent_test/test1.1.log\n```\n\nThe colon (`:`) in
